:661412908,"title":"为什么永中office也是国产且体验比wps好很多，用的人却不多呢？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/661412908","type":"question","created":1720765999,"answer_count":46,"follower_count":108,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[8459,213569,214086,3304529],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"今天终于把wps卸载了，换成了永中office。感觉wps已经彻底走向邪路了。虽然现在广告少了，但是基础功能都得是付费使用，并且强制登陆账号，不登录总是弹出来，影响使用。还有个烦人的问题是永远也不能干净的推出wps，总是悄悄登陆云服务。而且云服务还不随着wps的退出而退出。今天体验了一下永中office，我感觉我更愿意为永中office充会员，就算不充会员，永中office也不会一直弹窗，很安静，而且基础功能不需要登陆也能用，还有就是启动速度比wps快，且没有wps打开就要求登陆的界面，非常舒适，还有就是跟office没什么差别，无缝衔接。为什么这么好的国产office用的少呢？还有一个我特别讨厌wps的点是之前会员，稻壳会员，超级会员是可以同时开的，不小心同时开了，结果一个月的订阅，比office多好多，不知道现在有没有改进。"},"attached_info":"Cj8I1+abx/e0r4EjEAMaCTEwOTI1ODI5MyCvnMO0BjAAOGxABnIJNjYxNDEyOTA4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"127 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-fcc3b0de44564996a28f6618781a5120_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"7_1722417520.497349","card_id":"Q_663070265","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":663070265,"title":"怎么看待2024年7月31日A股市场行情走势？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/663070265","type":"question","created":1722399048,"answer_count":66,"follower_count":64,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[395,922,1740,3217,19800],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"怎么看待2024年7月31日A股市场行情走势？"},"attached_info":"Cj8I1+abx/e0r4EjEAMaCTEwOTYyNjY1NiDI8qa1BjAAOEBAB3IJNjYzMDcwMjY1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"118 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"childre