众相比，神里家和雷电五传受到的惩罚算什么？王侯将相，宁有种乎？自机角色的前代算人，惨死的npc不算人了？ Ps:我只相信善有善报恶有恶报，不是不报，时候未到。以上发言只针对本次节奏的始作俑者及各级代理，不针对被节奏卷入的任何人及随波逐流的任何人。"},"attached_info":"Cj8I1+abx/e0r4EjEAMaCTEwOTU0NTA4OSDxm5G1BjAAOBhAFHIJNjYyNzAyNjIyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"64 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"21_1722417520.503162","card_id":"Q_662292371","target":{"id":662292371,"title":"盛夏避暑，去哪里旅游合适？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/662292371","type":"question","created":1721642649,"answer_count":41,"follower_count":53,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[444,16126,24346,97999,409026],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I1+abx/e0r4EjEAMaCTEwOTQ1MzkyNiCZ3fi0BjAAODVAFXIJNjYyMjkyMzcxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"61 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"22_1722417520.503385","card_id":"Q_662590250","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":662590250,"title":"换了几个心理咨询师，对关系不再信任，还有换人咨询的必要吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/662590250","type":"question","created":1721932003,"answer_count":31,"follower_count":32,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[404,3877,5993,14990,26138],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"跟第二个咨询师断开后，很想他、给他留言，他回复下次谈谈，后一天我又想他，给他发了个可怜的表情包，他不回我了。我感觉再次被抛弃了。 跟第一个咨询师断开的时候，我也是找他留言，他都不理我。第一个进行了60次咨询，现在这个80次。第二个给我的忠告就是还是要找到且发现自己的爱好，变得有价值，才能获得朋友关系，我很绝望，我根本没有那个动力，我现在就是一个无聊的状态，兴趣爱好都找了几年了，都是坚持不下去，交不到朋友，